divs: sighting details1- i was recording two airplane with an iphone 5 while my husband worked on his car. reason 2-3- i didn't notice it while recording,later on when i checked the video i saw it. i had a friend of mine that is employed by the military, to take a look at it an examine it. he told me that the video was incredible ( i didn't think so) . he stopped it frame by frame, used all the tools at his disposal to find out what it could be. his. conclusions were: not military, not a big or dust on the camera etc. , he said it was an oval dark flying ship. i wish i could disclose his name, but he can't cause of his job. 4- it was going almost straight across the sky, but to even being able to see it on the video i had to considerably slow it down, and even than is incredibly fast! 5- since i didn't see it at the time of the recording, i'm gonna say n\a 6- since it was a "lucky catch", i would have never seen it at all if it wasn't for those 2 airplanes i was recording. i included different speeds of the the same video. the last video is the original. toward the end there is another dark object but its just a big black bird. thank you.
